<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><rss xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" version="2.0"><channel><title>World News, Today World News, Latest International News, World Breaking News, Trending News of World - Times of India</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>World News Today: Read the latest world news headlines, Current International breaking news world wide. In depth analysis and top news headlines world wide.</description><language>en-gb</language><lastBuildDate>2026-07-19T20:37:07+05:30</lastBuildDate><atom:link type="application/rss+xml" rel="self" href="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/rssfeeds/296589292.cms"/><copyright>Copyright:(C) Sun, 19 Jul 2026 20:37:07 IST Bennett Coleman &amp; Co. Ltd, http://in.indiatimes.com/policyterms/1554651.cms</copyright><docs>http://syndication.indiatimes.com/</docs><image><title>World News, Today World News, Latest International News, World Breaking News, Trending News of World - Times of India</title><url>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/507610.cms</url><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link></image><item><title><![CDATA[DNA from 457 koalas suggests the species nearly went extinct 100,000 years ago, before humans...]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132494936.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Approximately 100,000 years ago, koalas faced near extinction due to brutal ice ages. A recent genetic study triumphantly highlights that this crisis occurred well before humans populated Australia. By examining koala genomes, scientists have beautifully illustrated how climate shifts triggered significant declines in their population. Presently, however, modern threats stem largely from human activities, underscoring the urgent need for dedicated conservation measures.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/science/dna-from-457-koalas-suggests-the-species-nearly-went-extinct-100000-years-ago-before-humans-reached-australia/articleshow/132494936.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/science/dna-from-457-koalas-suggests-the-species-nearly-went-extinct-100000-years-ago-before-humans-reached-australia/articleshow/132494936.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-19T19:07:15+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI Science Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132495493,imgsize-305610.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA['That's what Lindsey wanted': Trump seeks Iran's inclusion in Russia sanctions bill]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132496481.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[President Trump wants Republican lawmakers to add Iran to the Russia sanctions bill. This legislation targets major buyers of Russian energy and aims to hold them accountable. The revised bill refines tariff authority and adds new measures for sanctions evasion. It also incorporates acts targeting Chinese support for Russia's defense industry. The updated legislation seeks to prevent Tehran from acquiring nuclear weapons.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/thats-what-lindsey-wanted-trump-seeks-irans-inclusion-in-russia-sanctions-bill/articleshow/132496481.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/thats-what-lindsey-wanted-trump-seeks-irans-inclusion-in-russia-sanctions-bill/articleshow/132496481.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-19T20:19:10+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132496489,imgsize-892474.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Saudi Arabia records 22.5% rise in Umrah arrivals as over 1.27 million pilgrims visit kingd